  "description": {
    "zh": "Polikhim厂区的流浪汉？你是说那个前安全副官？是，我认识他。这摊烂事给他造成了巨大的伤害——他开始酗酒，变成了流浪汉。但这不意味着他就是个坏人……等一下，他自己不能来说这些么？他被人干掉了？ 好吧，这已经不重要了，显然，既然你问了，这里确实有些问题。恩，我知道他住在哪里，但是我不会白白告诉你，因为我需要人帮我吓走海关里的拾荒者。如果你帮我，我就告诉你这个流浪汉原来住在哪里。",
    "en": "Polikhim hobo? The former deputy chief of security? Yes, I knew him. All this mess caused him some massive damage - took to drinking, degraded to a hobo. He's not a bad guy... Wait a sec, can’t he say for himself? Did he get whacked or something? Well, doesn't matter, but if you're asking about him, then there are some problems. Well, I knew where he lived, but here’s the deal - I need help scaring off the Scavs from the Customs. If you help me, I’ll tell you where this hobo lived."
  },
